            <lg xml:id="TK677">
<l>ceyviṉai ceyvāṉ ceyaṉmuṟai yavviṉai </l>
<l>yuḷḷaṟivā ṉuḷḷaṅ koḷal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The method of performance for one who has begun an act is to ascertain the mind of him who knows the secret thereof</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
